hopobject.body: Where do you study? owlstone medical london Acutely conscious of the media's interest in his love life and eager to prevent his girlfriend from being hounded by photographers like his late mother, Wills and Kate kept their relationship low-key, confiding in only a handful of trusted friends. They never left their university home together, arrived at social events separately and did not hold hands in public. Future Queen Catherine, Kate Middleton is pictured here in 2006 at age 24.
